C               **  NOTE THAT     ILEFT     IS THE NAME OF THE VARIABLE *
C               **  ON THE LEFT.                                        *
C               **  NOTE THAT     ILISTL    IS THE LINE IN THE TABLE    *
C               **  OF THE NAME ON THE LEFT.                            *
C               **  NOTE THAT     ICOLL    IS THE DATA COLUMN (1 TO 12) *
C               **  FOR THE NAME OF THE LEFT.                           *
C               *********************************************************
